	Yuan is a protoco for transmit message between two network entities. 
It is used with google protobuf. Yuan is in the form of byte stream, 
and variable length, including fixed length header and variable length payload. 
	The header is fixed length(12 bytes). composed of magic code (4bytes), 
id (4bytes), payload length(4 bytes).
	The payload is variable length bytes, following the header.

features:
	- running in a thread
	- async
